OL,3,C'Leave Portsmouth alone': Council's
OL,4,Cmessage to government
OL,6,FThe leader of Portsmouth City Council
OL,7,Fhas told central government to 'leave
OL,8,FPortsmouth alone' after it was told it
OL,9,Fmay have to merge with other councils
OL,10,Fin Hampshire.
OL,12,FCouncil Steve Pitt wrote to the
OL,13,FMinister of State for Local Government
OL,14,F& English Devolution, Jim McMahon,
OL,15,Ftoday (17 April) to outline the
OL,16,Fcouncil's position on government
OL,17,Freorganisation.
