OL,3,C'Leave Portsmouth alone': Council's
OL,4,Cmessage to government
OL,6,FEarlier this year Hampshire County
OL,7,FCouncil, Southampton City Council,
OL,8,FPortsmouth City Council and the Isle
OL,9,Fof Wight Council all voted to join the
OL,10,Fgovernment's Priority Devolution
OL,11,FProgramme.
OL,13,FAs part of this, the government then
OL,14,Fasked all councils to draw up plans on
OL,15,Fhow they could reorganise, to create
OL,16,Ffinancially stable and sustainable new
OL,17,Funitary authorities.
