OL,3,C'Leave Portsmouth alone': Council's
OL,4,Cmessage to government
OL,6,FAny reorganisation, he said, would not
OL,7,Fbe in the interests of Portsmouth's
OL,8,F210,000 residents and would lead to
OL,9,Fless financial stability.
OL,11,F"The government is arguing we are too
OL,12,Fsmall and can be more financially
OL,13,Fstable through Local Government
OL,14,FReorganisation but there is no
OL,15,Fevidence for that", he said.
OL,17,F"We have disproved their arguments and
OL,18,Fcontinue to tell Government that
OL,19,FPortsmouth City Council does not need
OL,20,Fto be part of any reorganisation.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
