OL,3,C'Leave Portsmouth alone': Council's
OL,4,Cmessage to government
OL,6,FHowever, Portsmouth City Council has
OL,7,Fdrawn up proposals on the creation of
OL,8,Fa new 'South East Hampshire' council.
OL,10,FThe authority would meet the
OL,11,Fgovernment's 500,000 population target
OL,12,Ffor new councils, which are set to be
OL,13,Fcreated as Hampshire devolves.
OL,15,FCllr Pitt said it has been drawn up to
OL,16,Fensure Portsmouth has the 'best
OL,17,Foutcome', as the council has been told
OL,18,Fgovernment will impose reorganisation
OL,19,Feven if proposals are not submitted,
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
