OL,3,C'Leave Portsmouth alone': Council's
OL,4,Cmessage to government
OL,6,FThe 'South East Hampshire' council
OL,7,Fwould cover Portsmouth, Fareham,
OL,8,FGosport, Havant and could also absorb
OL,9,Fparts of Winchester City Council and
OL,10,FEast Hampshire Council.
OL,12,FCllr Pitt said: "The area covered by
OL,13,FPortsmouth, Southampton and Hampshire
OL,14,Fis huge and needs a minimum of four
OL,15,Fseparate councils to support
OL,16,Fresidents, but this should really be
OL,17,Flooking at where communities exist and
OL,18,Fhow best they are supported.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
