OL,3,C'Leave Portsmouth alone': Council's
OL,4,Cmessage to government
OL,6,F"People don't live their lives within
OL,7,Fcouncil boundaries drawn on a map
OL,8,Fdecades ago, and we need to make sure,
OL,9,Fif Government forces change on us, it
OL,10,Fis done in a way that best meets
OL,11,Fresidents needs based on the areas
OL,12,Fthey identify with and use."
OL,14,FThe department for Ministry of
OL,15,FHousing, Communities & Local
OL,16,FGovernment has been contacted for
OL,17,Fcomment.
